high_descs: Turn around, go to the fridge, then go to the sink right of the fridge.
Take the glass out of the cabinet above the sink.
Bring the glass to the fridge on the left of the sink.
Chill the glass in the fridge.
Take the chilled glass to the stove on the right.
Put the chilled glass in the thin cabinet left of the stove, down below.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled glass in the cabinet left of stove.

high_descs: Turn around, hang a right at the fridge, walk to the sink on the left and look up at the cabinets.
Open the left cabinet, pick up the martini glass from inside and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the black fridge on the right.
Put the glass inside the fridge on the top shelf in between the plates, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the white stove ahead.
Open the lower cabinet to the left of the stove, put the chilled glass inside and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled glass in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around, walk forward past table, turn right, walk forward halfway length of table, turn left, walk forward to sink, look up
Open cupboard above sink, grab glass from cupboard
Turn left, walk to wall, turn right facing refrigerator
Open refrigerator, place glass on shelf, close refrigerator, open refrigerator, remove glass, close refrigerator
Turn right, walk forward to oven
Open cupboard on left side of oven, place glass inside cupboard, close cupboard
anns.task_desc: Move glass from upper cupboard to lower cupboard
